{"tid":757009,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗和稅務局達成一致，他將認罪並繳納1900萬歐元以免坐牢","createTime":"2018-07-26T12:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T06:50:27.000Z","uid":20634,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"687fba278818d49cfd44526f5cb083323e65159e","tid":757009,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:48:34.000Z","msg":"西班牙埃菲社消息，西班牙稅務局和C朗終於就逃稅案的處罰達成了一致，後者將支付1900萬歐元，另外還有兩年的入獄刑罰，但根據西班牙法律，初犯且刑罰在兩年及以下的個人不需要真正服刑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.dongqiudi.com/fastdfs3/M00/37/48/ChOxM1tZuZmAPRYEAAJu4f_Tpk4914.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.dongqiudi.com%2Ffastdfs3%2FM00%2F37%2F48%2FChOxM1tZuZmAPRYEAAJu4f_Tpk4914.jpg&h=4b0a7fcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來自司法部門的消息告知埃菲社雙方已經達成一致，只要C朗承認犯下四項財務上的罪行，並且付清款項，就可以免除牢獄之災。<br />\n<br />\n稅務局控告C朗在2011至2014年間逃稅1477萬歐元，其中2011年139萬歐元，2012年166萬歐元，2013年320萬歐元，2014年850萬歐元。在經過長時間的協商後，檢察院將逃稅數字降低到570萬歐元，但是加上罰款和利息，C朗總計要支付1900萬歐元。他還需要支付相關法律部門在此過程的花費。"},{"pid":"fbb6a7f657d4c67d5952d93fa79147d1cfe2ac53","tid":757009,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:54:11.000Z","msg":"一年交850萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cbd3fc4988ab825fdf78b9f884a21dfdb123bb3","tid":757009,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbb6a7f657d4c67d5952d93fa79147d1cfe2ac53","tid":757009,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:54:11.000Z","msg":"一年交850萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:56:02.000Z","msg":"捐比山區兒童好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa74301cd7d6a68791e7c6f2cc013fd45e1ed271","tid":757009,"uid":16086,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:47:51.000Z","msg":"美欺又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgm